These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, february
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, ivory
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, pop
House: farmhouse, townhouse
City: new-york, edinburgh
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, skateboard
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, tiparillo
1. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
5. the tiparillo-smoker is the fan of pop##1
6. the townhouse house is the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Birthday      | february        | april |
| Color          | ivory  | azure     |
| Music-Genre         | pop    | r&b         |
| House           | farmhouse    | townhouse |
| City   | new-york  | edinburgh     |
| Transport           | skateboard      | trike    |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | davidoff          |

