.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-2::.
House: futuristic, colonial
2 different games are played: scrabble, poker
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, soccer
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, amaryllis
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, baccarat
There 2 different types of food: spinach, pineapple
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| House         | futuristic      | colonial       |
| Game           | scrabble | poker |
| Beverage   | water      | almond-milk        |
| Sport   | skiing         | soccer        |
| Flower   | aconite    | amaryllis       |
| Cigar           | baccarat        | dunhill          |
| Food     | pineapple          | spinach    |

