2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the fan of techno is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Music-Genre      | gospel | techno  |
